Description: The flight into Egypt; in the foreground, the Holy Family crosses a river at centre; village and castle on a rock at the right shore; mountainous landscape background; trimmed below. 1558 Etching
Curator's comments: Part of a series of landscapes with Biblical subjects, consisting of five plates (Hollstein 40-44).
Bibliographic references: Hollstein / German engravings, etchings and woodcuts c.1400-1700 (42)
Acquisition name: Purchased from: A E Evans & Sons
